title: Down Goes Arizona and Gonzaga!
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss Michigan’s tourney run ending in the Sweet 16. Jalen take about what this Michigan season means to him. Gonzaga and Arizona go down. Jacoby’s pick the Houston Cougars proved him right as they pull the upset. And no more putting down the Phoenix Suns! They are the best team in the NBA. Chris Paul makes his return for the Suns and they clinch the number 1 spot in the Western Conference. Let’s show them some love! All that and much more.
